title: The Day Grunge Died: A Kurt Cobain Live Stream Tribute 2017
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: sorry I couldn't be here at the life stream :(
description:
For me and thousands of other fans, grunge music died the day Kurt Cobain left this mortal coil. Everyone is welcome to chat live about Kurt, Nirvana, and any topic that comes to their mind as we approach 23 years since the day grunge died.

Hosts include MaryGirl Moody and Tami Sifford.

ASSHOLES ARE WELCOMED, DICKHOLES ARE BANNED.
